review:
Went here for wisdom tooth extraction. Dr Gopi explained about the procedure and made me to feel comfortable. After a much acceptable wait time the actualprocedure was performed. It's all in one sitting. Surprising!! Is it not? It was my first visit and all done in an hour. And when it comes to pocket they are much much friendly. 
I suggest this clinic with no hesitation. A big thanks to all the friendly staff.

review:

Dr. Gopinath is well experienced and to the point. He explained us why is the treatment needed, how is it done and what precautions to take etc. In every appointment he made sure we are comfortable and getting the right treatment done.
They do followup calls to check how the condition time to time. Overall we had a very good experience *** **** ** *** *** **** ** ** *** ** *** **** ******* **** ** **********
